(79, 1, '2018-05-11 12:17:53', '2018-05-11 12:17:53', 'Whether it\'s extending your presence on the internet or developing other web services, our team can help with:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Graphic and web design</li>\r\n 	<li>HTML5 and CSS</li>\r\n 	<li>HTML Emails</li>\r\n 	<li>PHP (Zend, Magento, Wordpress)</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Web Technologies', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'web-technologies', '', '', '2018-05-11 12:17:53', '2018-05-11 12:17:53', '', 0, 'http://badinsoft.milosevicm.com/?post_type=technologies&#038;p=79', 0, 'technologies', '', 0),
(80, 1, '2018-05-11 12:18:12', '2018-05-11 12:18:12', 'There is an app for everything, literally. We know that our clients most of the time need a mobile app too, to successfully run their business\', so we are able to provide the apps for the most popular platforms:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Android</li>\r\n 	<li>iOS</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Mobile Technologies', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mobile-technologies', '', '', '2018-05-11 12:18:12', '2018-05-11 12:18:12', '', 0, 'http://badinsoft.milosevicm.com/?post_type=technologies&#038;p=80', 0, 'technologies', '', 0),
(81, 1, '2018-05-11 12:18:31', '2018-05-11 12:18:31', 'As the world quickly transforms and technology momentum doesn\'t slow down, more than ever there is a need for efficient project management. To keep the quality of our products and services at a high level and work fast, we are using the Agile approach in our business. Because of that, next to developers, in our team we have people who do:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Software Architecture</li>\r\n 	<li>Project Management and Administration</li>\r\n 	<li>Team and Project Coordination</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Agile Approach', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'agile-approach', '', '', '2018-05-11 12:18:31', '2018-05-11 12:18:31', '', 0, 'http://badinsoft.milosevicm.com/?post_type=technologies&#038;p=81', 0, 'technologies', '', 0),
(82, 1, '2018-05-11 12:18:50', '2018-05-11 12:18:50', 'A dedicated team of system administrators and DevOps is responsible for making sure our products are secure and work like clockwork.\r\n\r\nThat includes:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Server setup and maintenance (Windows/Linux)</li>\r\n 	<li>Maintenance of cloud infrastructure and virtual environments (Amazon AWS/VMware/KVM/Docker)</li>\r\n 	<li>Installation and maintenance of application and web services (Tomcat, Apache, Nginx, IIS)</li>\r\n 	<li>Maintenance of infrastructure services (Active Directory, DNS, DHCP, WSUS, Group policies)</li>\r\n 	<li>Maintenance and setup of network services (IPSec VPN, OpenVPN)</li>\r\n 	<li>Maintenance and setup of monitoring services (– Zabbix, Nagios, MRTG)</li>\r\n 	<li>Maintenance and setup of email services (– Exchange, Office365 Cloud, Postfix)</li>\r\n 	<li>Installation and configuration of RDBMS: Oracle, PostGre, MySql, DB2</li>\r\n 	<li>Pl/SQL, pg/SQL stored procedures, TAPI/MAPI</li>\r\n 	<li>Oracle based: RAC, TAF, FAN, load balance, security, optimization, Backup strategies. Disaster &amp; Recovery, GoldenGate, OAS, IAS, Forms &amp; Reports ETL</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Infrastructure', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'infrastructure', '', '', '2018-05-11 12:18:50', '2018-05-11 12:18:50', '', 0, 'http://badinsoft.milosevicm.com/?post_type=technologies&#038;p=82', 0, 'technologies', '', 0),
