(100, 1, '2018-05-14 10:58:17', '2018-05-14 10:58:17', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Badin Soft is a relatively young IT company located in Niš, the southeastern IT center of Serbia. It was founded only five years ago with a vision that the idea of <em>\"improving everyday life using knowledge and hard work\"</em> is achievable. Founded by two people who see the world as a set of opportunities instead of obstacles, Badin Soft became a part of the Serbian branch of Transactortech and thus made its first international steps. Slowly but surely, Badin Soft continued to grow, employing people whose vision of the world entails technology being used and developed to help people around the globe. As our team continued to grow, a need for a new, larger space emerged. That space facilitated the achievement of another desire and idea of our founders - applying agile methodologies in everyday work.</span>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-101 aligncenter\" src=\"http://badinsoft.milosevicm.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/group_photo.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"3998\" height=\"2250\" />\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As our company continued to grow, in November 2016, Badin Soft was officially registered as LLT. Shortly thereafter, this newly established company signed a contract with its largest client, Tranxactor New Zealand Ltd. The adventure of conquering other continents continues with the establishment of successful co-operation in Europe, Asia, and Australia. Today, Badin Soft works with prestigious Swiss fintech and banking companies, the most famous of which is Crealogix (through a partnership with Pannonia Expertise), as well as with many companies through the development of systems and applications that support consumer loyalty programs - the world-famous Subway, Westfield, Customer Radar and the likes. Some of our significant domestic clients are Telekom Srbija and Asseco, whose trust we earned through hard work and quality cooperation.</span>\n\n<img class=\"wp-image-66 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"http://badinsoft.milosevicm.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/timeline.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2369\" height=\"1169\" />\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Once small, but now a company with a numerous successful projects and cooperations behind itself, Badin Soft has managed to attract, employ and keep 50 employees and associates. The secret of this success lies in the trust that’s being shown to our employees every day, in respecting their opinion and in the belief that the same goal connects us all.</span>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img class=\"wp-image-99 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"http://badinsoft.milosevicm.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/employees3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" />\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We’ll remember the spring of 2018 as a period dedicated to moving to a new space in the center of the city. We’ll also remember it after continuing successful co-operations with the old and starting new ones with domestic and foreign clients.</span>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-102 size-full\" src=\"http://badinsoft.milosevicm.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/newspace1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1508\" height=\"999\" />\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;', 'Our Story', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '65-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-05-14 10:58:17', '2018-05-14 10:58:17', '', 65, 'http://badinsoft.milosevicm.com/2018/05/11/65-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
